{
  "id": "628ea303595067001fb17d42",
  "title": "Scrapboxは執筆に向いているか",
  "created": 1653515018,
  "updated": 1661418323,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "628ea303595067001fb17d42",
      "text": "Scrapboxは執筆に向いているか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515018,
      "updated": 1653515025
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea31079d3a90000cf2a28",
      "text": "#書いてけ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515025,
      "updated": 1653515026
    },
    {
      "id": "628eebcdaff09e00008e84cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533645,
      "updated": 1653533645
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea31679d3a90000cf2a2d",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515031,
      "updated": 1653515043
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea32279d3a90000cf2a2e",
      "text": " 執筆=5万文字以上のまとまった文章（[sta.icon]の経験は電子書籍、長文ブログ記事、リファレンスみたいなウェブサイト）を当該プラットフォームが要求するフォーマットで仕上げて公開する、としておく",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515043,
      "updated": 1653515106
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea36179d3a90000cf2a2f",
      "text": " ---",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515106,
      "updated": 1653515107
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea36a79d3a90000cf2a31",
      "text": "\tScrapboxは収束と発散でいう、",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515116,
      "updated": 1653515477
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea37079d3a90000cf2a32",
      "text": "\t\t発散で使う",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515120,
      "updated": 1653515123
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea37379d3a90000cf2a33",
      "text": "\t\t収束では使いづらい",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515123,
      "updated": 1653515126
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea37679d3a90000cf2a34",
      "text": "\t\tという印象[sta.icon][sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515127,
      "updated": 1653515485
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea31079d3a90000cf2a29",
      "text": "\t収束するときは「文章」を書いたり構造を並べたり（markdownでいうと大見出し中見出し小見出し）するのと、全体を俯瞰して雰囲気というか世界観と言うかそういうのを統一する必要があると思っているが、これがScrapboxでは難しい",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515025,
      "updated": 1653515210
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea3ca79d3a90000cf2a37",
      "text": "\t\t「ツールの力で俯瞰する」か「頭の中で展開するか」が必要",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515210,
      "updated": 1653515236
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea3e379d3a90000cf2a39",
      "text": "\t\t[sta.icon]は後者ができないので前者",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515236,
      "updated": 1653515285
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea41779d3a90000cf2a3d",
      "text": "\t\t\t[秀丸エディタのアウトライン]に頼っている",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515287,
      "updated": 1653515295
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea40e79d3a90000cf2a3b",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/809c46e720e8ef3c571203992ff0d0b6]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515279,
      "updated": 1653515280
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea4b279d3a90000cf2a44",
      "text": " \t\t\t本文の俯瞰と構造（見出しによる目次）の俯瞰ができる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515442,
      "updated": 1653515518
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea4c379d3a90000cf2a45",
      "text": " \t\t\talt + up/downで次/前の見出しにジャンプできる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515460,
      "updated": 1653515518
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea4fe79d3a90000cf2a46",
      "text": " \t\t[sta.icon]はこれと出会えたおかげで万文字の長文を書けるようになった（それまでは手が届かない夢だった）",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515519,
      "updated": 1653515542
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea40f79d3a90000cf2a3c",
      "text": "\t\tScrapboxだとこれができない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515280,
      "updated": 1653515318
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea43679d3a90000cf2a3e",
      "text": "\t\t\tページに分けると閲覧時に遷移が必要だし、遷移には（オンラインなので）かなり時間がかかる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515319,
      "updated": 1653515345
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea45079d3a90000cf2a3f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t0.x、いや0.0x秒で移ってくれないと[sta.icon]の脳内はすぐにコンテキストを忘れてしまう",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515345,
      "updated": 1653515365
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea3cf79d3a90000cf2a38",
      "text": "\t\t\tかといって1ページに全部書くと今度はスクロールに時間がかかる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515215,
      "updated": 1653515386
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea47a79d3a90000cf2a41",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t見出し単位でサクサク遷移する、みたいなことができない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515387,
      "updated": 1653515396
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea48a79d3a90000cf2a42",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tあと純粋に重くなる（1ページに10万文字書くとかはさすがに厳しい）",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515402,
      "updated": 1653515419
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea49a79d3a90000cf2a43",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tPCや回線の性能次第かもしれないが",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515419,
      "updated": 1653515424
    },
    {
      "id": "628ea46679d3a90000cf2a40",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653515367,
      "updated": 1653515367
    },
    {
      "id": "628eebf0aff09e00008e84d6",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533681,
      "updated": 1653533681
    },
    {
      "id": "628eebf1aff09e00008e84d7",
      "text": "\t[Scrapboxは執筆には向いていない]に書いた:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533681,
      "updated": 1653538596
    },
    {
      "id": "628eebf1aff09e00008e84d8",
      "text": "  Scrapboxは、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533681,
      "updated": 1653534173
    },
    {
      "id": "628eebf1aff09e00008e84d9",
      "text": " \t\t[有限の時間]で、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533681,
      "updated": 1653534173
    },
    {
      "id": "628eebf1aff09e00008e84da",
      "text": " \t\t有限のページ数の紙の書籍を、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533681,
      "updated": 1653534173
    },
    {
      "id": "628eebf1aff09e00008e84db",
      "text": " \t\tツリーで構築し、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533681,
      "updated": 1653534173
    },
    {
      "id": "628eebf1aff09e00008e84dc",
      "text": "  \tきれいに清書して完成させること",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533681,
      "updated": 1653534173
    },
    {
      "id": "628eebf1aff09e00008e84dd",
      "text": "  には向いていない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533681,
      "updated": 1653534175
    },
    {
      "id": "628eebf2aff09e00008e84de",
      "text": "　想定規模としては[エンジニアの知的生産術]が35文字32行244ページだから25万文字くらい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533682,
      "updated": 1653534454
    },
    {
      "id": "628eed6daff09e0000d68679",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653534062,
      "updated": 1653534062
    },
    {
      "id": "628eed6daff09e0000d6867a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653534062,
      "updated": 1653534062
    },
    {
      "id": "628eec09aff09e0000d68678",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/c29f8bf33c10fc801bd2eeb7d43befe3]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533705,
      "updated": 1653533728
    },
    {
      "id": "628eebf2aff09e00008e84df",
      "text": "\t[https://cyblog.jp/33884 Scrapboxについての本をScrapboxで書きました | シゴタノ！]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533682,
      "updated": 1653533743
    },
    {
      "id": "628eec2faff09e00008e84e1",
      "text": "  >もともと[構造志向のツール]ではないので、「めちゃくちゃ本作りに向いている！」とはさすがに言えませんが、それでもやってやれなくないことは確かです。足りない機能に関しては（ある程度までなら）UserScriptで補うこともできます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533743,
      "updated": 1653533775
    },
    {
      "id": "628eec07aff09e0000d68677",
      "text": "　UserScriptで補ってる機能としては「ページ目次のメニューを作る」などがある、頑張ってるなぁ[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653533704,
      "updated": 1653534350
    },
    {
      "id": "628eee8eaff09e000005cd57",
      "text": "　 自分でこういうスクリプトを作れる人は「執筆」をする人の中ではレア",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653534350,
      "updated": 1653534385
    },
    {
      "id": "628f366c79d3a9000091c0cf",
      "text": "\t　 +1[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653552749,
      "updated": 1653552752
    },
    {
      "id": "628eee4faff09e000005cd56",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653534287,
      "updated": 1653534287
    },
    {
      "id": "628ef3b15b98c200001a7e72",
      "text": " [/daiiz/Pimento Cloud]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1653535665,
      "updated": 1653535674
    },
    {
      "id": "628ef4495b98c200001a7e75",
      "text": "  [daiiz.icon]さん作の書籍執筆支援ツール",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1653535817,
      "updated": 1653535886
    },
    {
      "id": "628ef4565b98c200001a7e76",
      "text": "  ScrapboxをTeXに変換してPDFをつくるというツール [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1653535831,
      "updated": 1653535831
    },
    {
      "id": "628ef3e45b98c200001a7e74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1653535716,
      "updated": 1653535716
    },
    {
      "id": "63073b52e60035000093b7cb",
      "text": "[執筆ツール]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1661418323,
      "updated": 1661418323
